annotations: I was standing out side waiting for my ride to work and a cluster of ufos that looked like sides ways glowing black eyed peas. Maybe 12 of them they moved very quick and vanished just as fast as they showed up. No noises and a very clear night. No idea it’s my first time seeing something like that. I wanna talk to people about it but people around here will think I’m nuts. But I’m not going to lie I’m shook.
